# SatTrack — Frontend Rules

## Vue / TypeScript Style
- Always `<script setup lang="ts">` — never omit `lang="ts"`
- Composables over options API
- File names: `kebab-case.vue` components, `camelCase.ts` composables
- Types: interfaces for data shapes, type aliases for unions

## UnoCSS
- Pure utility classes — no `@apply`
- Custom shortcuts in `uno.config.ts` for repeated patterns
- Color palette: `space-*` (dark backgrounds), `primary-*` (accent)

## Components Map
```
components/
├── common/         ObservationLocation · SatellitePassCard · PassPredictData · CombinedSatelliteData · MobileNav · ChevronIcon
├── pass-predict/   PolarPlot (SVG) · PassCard · PassDetails · PassHeader
├── ar-track/       ArPolarPlot (compass-rotated SVG) · ArIndicators (EL/AZ overlay)
└── settings/       AdditionalSettings · ApiCredentials · SatelliteManagement · StorageManagement · CombinedDataDisplay
```

## Pass Predict Composables (`composables/pass-predict/`)
- `usePassData.ts` — fetch + store pass list
- `usePassStatus.ts` — active/upcoming/past state
- `useRealTimePosition.ts` — N2YO polling during active pass
- `useSatellitePath.ts` — arc path for SVG polar plot
- `usePolarPlotBackground.ts` — static SVG background (circles, labels)
- `usePassFiltering.ts` — filter by satellite/elevation
- `usePassCleanup.ts` — cleanup timers/intervals

## Storage Composables (`composables/storage/`)
- `useSettings.ts` — location + preferences in IndexedDB
- `useIndexedDB.ts` — IndexedDB CRUD wrapper
- `useSecureStorage.ts` — AES-encrypted credential storage

## AR Tracking
- `useDeviceOrientation.ts` — wraps `DeviceOrientationEvent`
  - `alpha` = compass 0–360° True North · `beta` = pitch ±180° · `gamma` = roll ±90°
  - iOS 13+: explicit permission handled internally
- `ArPolarPlot.vue` — SVG rotated by compass (up = where device points)
- `ArIndicators.vue` — EL/AZ overlay

## GPS Settings
- `enableHighAccuracy` respects user toggle
- timeout: `30000` ms (GPS cold start), maximumAge: `60000` ms
- Fallback: low accuracy + maximumAge `300000`

## Types (`types/`)
- `satellite.d.ts` — `TLEData`, `PassPrediction`, `SatellitePosition`
- `api.d.ts` — N2YO, SatNOGS, Space-Track response shapes
- `storage.d.ts` — IndexedDB schema, settings shape
- `global.d.ts` — global extensions
